Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.57,0:01:11.33,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}In the memory of a far off day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.64,0:01:18.18,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}the story of the blue country bloomed
