Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.59,0:01:40.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The other star has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:43.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A round of applause for this brave merchant!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.49,0:01:48.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H575F66&\4c&H575F66&\pos(640,504)\blur3\1c&HCCD4DD&}Wolf and Unbridged Divide
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:50.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat my declaration!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:54.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall repay the debt that that is shouldered by the traveling nun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:01:57.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And when she has been granted freedom...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.42,0:02:02.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the name of St. Lambardos who watches over the Rowen Trading Guild from above,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:06.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear that I shall profess my sincere love to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:11.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo already told me of her misfortune and the how she has been treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:17.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will use my social standing and fortunes to restore the feathers of freedom to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.43,0:02:19.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and then propose to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:21.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A seal of blood, and that knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:21.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're serious, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:27.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if her debt is paid off, Horo won't necessarily stop traveling with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:29.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am confident that she will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:32.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, Horo is, while not perfect, still a nun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:33.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Marriage is—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:37.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo does not belong to any convent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:41.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she's just a nun out of convenience while traveling,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:45.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,she isn't bound by the clergy to any oaths forbidding marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:47.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've done your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:53.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,According to Kumerson city law, when a woman is in debt, her guardian holds the rights as creditor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:58.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to unconditionally accede to my marriage proposal,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:03:00.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,we could settle this without a contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:02.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:05.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you take the contract knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.02,0:03:06.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away, Lawrence!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.47,0:03:08.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be shameful as a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:11.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:17.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,1000 Trenni silver?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:23.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will repay you the sum that Horo owes you before evening tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.86,0:03:26.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake in the expiry period, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:27.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.11,0:03:29.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,1000 Trenni silver in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:33.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't accept any bargaining or loans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:35.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:38.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:42.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the contract is established.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:45.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet here again tomorrow, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:50.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:53.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For something as trivial as having her debts paid,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:56.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,my companion won't be swayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:04:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Double for Lawrence, four times for Amarty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,5 Iredo on Lawrence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:03.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm putting 12 Iredo on you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:08.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bartose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:10.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you've gotten involved in something troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:12.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.67,0:04:17.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe Amarty has come up with a way to make good on the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:18.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And likely,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:21.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,not a particularly tasteful way either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:27.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be too pitiable for Amarty if I were to help you too much, so I won't go into the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:31.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.47,0:04:32.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:37.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because no matter the reason, having someone to travel with is a happy thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:40.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Having that taken from you would be too harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:46.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do if that boy hands over the 1000 silver?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:50.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After settling the money you've spent, I'd give you the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:54.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't test me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:58.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If Amarty is able to complete the contract, I'd hold up my end of the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.85,0:04:59.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:00.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a bit of confidence you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:01.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:04.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I simply trust in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:07.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:09.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're much cuter when you're panicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:12.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quite impressed with how much I've grown, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:15.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you're grown-up because you stay calm and composed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:16.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:21.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you simply analyze the odds, then find they're in your favor and act all smug...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:23.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just plain scheming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:26.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Call it a merchant's skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:31.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Refusing Amarty's contract would also have been an elegant way out, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:32.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:36.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you made your decision after judging the reactions of the onlookers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:40.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's think about how it'd be if our roles were reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:42.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Reversed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:48.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay by Lawrence's side forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:53.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm in debt, it's a bond that connects the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:05:57.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be able to endure that link being severed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:00.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I am to be put to shame right here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:03.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot accept that contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:06.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:11.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's definitely a manly way of handling it, but whether it's grown-up or not is a different matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.34,0:06:18.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, while it's true I'd be happy, that's only something a youngster without regard for consequences would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:19.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be overdoing it. {Literally: like a burp coming out}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:26.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think about it that way, maybe manly behavior and grown-up behavior can't mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:30.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A proper man appears childish, and a proper grown-up appears cowardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:36.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, how would the womanly and grown-up sage wolf Horo respond to that situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:38.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd smile and take it, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:41.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then after accepting the contract and returning to the inn,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd kneel like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:50.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you agreed because you thought it was a good gamble,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:55.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but you'll undoubtedly make additional moves in the shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:58.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like back door dealings and misinformation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:01.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to take you to the festival, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:05.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A merchant wouldn't hesitate to bribe in order to fulfill a contract, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.67,0:07:08.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:10.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking the rumored beauty around with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:15.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I kept her locked up in the inn, I'd really look like I was using her debt to tie her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:19.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...says Lawrence, but what's the truth of the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:20.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the whole truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:23.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am bound by the fetters of an enormous debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:28.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,These chains are so heavy that I could not escape no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:34.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you could undo them for me, I would be happy to dirty myself with flour.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:38.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder Amarty fell head over heels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:42.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The real one being tied down is definitely Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.26,0:07:42.11,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:44.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:48.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:49.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:53.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... there's 200 Iredo in taxes recorded in the tax ledger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:58.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means, as far as the city council is aware of,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:00.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amarty has about 800 Trenni silver worth of assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:02.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of gambling is there here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:06.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cards, dice, and Hare and Hounds {http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hare_and_Hounds_%28Board_Game%29}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:06.21,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Wiki "Hare and Hounds (Board Game)"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:08.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s also a limit on the stakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:17.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of gambling, I heard that in the case that Amarty wins, there's also bets on which one of you will win after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:18.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:22.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now you have the advantage at a 1.2 to 1 payoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:24.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:26.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have the banker share some of the earnings with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:29.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's the real situation like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.31,0:08:33.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when there's an answer, there are some questions in this world that can't be answered easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:36.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:38.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,the purity of that flour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:45.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What would I do if my debts were cleared?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:47.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you want to ask, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:50.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, that'd be unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:55.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that's the case, the only thing we can do is observe the opponent's actions directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:56.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How sneaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:58.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Call it an underwater battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:04.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he'll definitely send people to watch my every move as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:05.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:09.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Amarty was originally the heir of a rich family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:14.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He left home and came to this remote region, with a will as strong as his sense for profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:20.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks down on the way the rest of us form connections with other merchants in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:23.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He made it this far on his own strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:25.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's almost like a heroic knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:28.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:33.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's exactly why he fell for a charming nun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.35,0:09:38.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, the women of town have an even stronger bond amongst themselves than we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:40.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't take well to outsiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:43.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he'd be able to deal with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:43.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:46.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:49.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm free to make use of my connections.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:56.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be sneaky for a knight, but in a battle between merchants there are no such complaints.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:10:00.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In the meantime, could you continue gathering information?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:04.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bartose seems to think Amarty has a way to collect the funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:08.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If the contract goes unfulfilled, you won't have to continue worrying about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:09.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And if all goes well,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:13.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just might be able to make a profit from Amarty's scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:24.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that a shepherd's horn just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:25.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:27.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't normally be blown in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:30.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If that shepherdess girl had followed us here, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:33.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing much. I'd just greet her with "How unexpected!".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:37.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't get flustered then it looks like I'm trying to win you over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:42.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well that's just delightful. So much so that it's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:45.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, the festival just started.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:48.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:51.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just eating is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:03.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:05.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:16.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We get front-row seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:18.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We should thank Amarty for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:27.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a splendid act.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:30.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And the atmosphere isn't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:18.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's join them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:24.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:28.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful not to step on my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:29.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:40.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:42.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bed's next.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:44.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little further.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:45.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:47.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be gentle to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.19,0:12:48.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:08.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:13.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A letter from Mark arrived for you while you were out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:14.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,From Mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:19.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It can wait till tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe not...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:25.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for waking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:29.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to go meet Mark again for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:32.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With a female-scented letter hidden in your jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:34.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:36.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything else you're hiding from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.43,0:13:42.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, yesterday, I met with someone familiar with legends from the north and asked about Yoitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:44.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She happened to be a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:46.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:48.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I got some worthwhile information from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:50.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I also heard a story about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:51.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:52.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes. {added}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:54.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a legend about you in Renose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"We called her 'Horou of the wheaten tail'."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.26,0:13:58.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:00.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:04.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The legend spoke about which direction you came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:07.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:09.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:12.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you came from a forest east of Renose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.84,0:14:18.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Southwest of Niohira and east of Renose, in the mountains, is apparently where Yoitsu is located.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:24.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you hiding that so you could surprise me later?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:28.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you had told me sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:30.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:35.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When all we knew was that it was southwest of Niohira, it would've been hard to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:36.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But with this, we've narrowed it down quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:38.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect this letter holds additional information.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:41.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we might arrive sooner than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:43.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. {added}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:53.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we got to Niohira, wouldn't you be able to go back alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:15:01.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it takes half a year, let's do our best to find it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:11.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll going to go see Mark now, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.21,0:15:14.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With that female-scented letter in your pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:27.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty relaxed for someone who's asking others to help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:29.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Lawrence?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:32.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I do have a lot of free time during the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:35.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm making quite a bit thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:38.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You took advantage of it? What's the scheme?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.61,0:15:40.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was easy money, I raked it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:45.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew as soon as you said Bartose had an idea of what the scheme was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:47.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Precious stones?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:49.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Close, but not quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:53.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't really call what we're dealing in "precious stones".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:55.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pyrite?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:58.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you already knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:15:59.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about the fortune telling, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:00.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.90,0:16:02.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But that that fellow's not in town any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.39,0:16:07.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly she attracted the attention of the Inquisition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:10.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The town would be in mayhem if the church had really come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:11.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:14.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's too much pyrite going around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:18.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet she bought it in bulk from some town and disappeared once it sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:23.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And thanks to the fortune teller's sales pitch, the church is after them, so its value is skyrocketing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:26.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you think it's worth right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:27.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:29.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Guessing liberally, 100?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:30.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,270.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:31.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:35.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a stupid price, but when the market opens tomorrow I expect it'll rise even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:38.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, this goes for 270?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:44.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even worthless junk, given a story that they have some effect, will go for a high price.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:47.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The women of the town are crazy about these right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.33,0:16:54.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're competing over how much they can get wealthy traders and farmers to spend on the miracle stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:58.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time they plead the price goes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:02.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To think this would become such a huge business...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:05.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're no longer talking about profit in mere percentages here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:07.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking several or even ten times the return.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.18,0:17:11.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that Amarty is likely raking in the money faster than lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:17.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I only just got into it and I've already made 300 Iredo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:20.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody wants to let this one out on their watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:23.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else knows about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:25.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to have spread throughout the marketplace this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.22,0:17:28.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,While you and the princess were dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.87,0:17:32.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,there was already a huge ruckus in front of the ore merchant stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:34.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've failed as a merchant...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:37.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can still pull through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:41.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With all the merchants running amok for these, the prices have skyrocketed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:42.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:46.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,if by chance you fail, you'll have the money to buy a new princess, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:53.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, for now I’ll be buying some of these from you using the credit from the nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:57.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, are things really okay with you and the princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:18:01.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amarty might just be able to buy out her debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.96,0:18:03.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:06.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With the money from this deal, I'll make more profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.53,0:18:11.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, chosen by the now-free princess, I'll resume my journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:12.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite some confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:14.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.21,0:18:25.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You... can read?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:26.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:30.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:34.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer have a home to go back to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:38.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.31,0:18:42.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only an old story.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:44.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of those legends are inaccurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:46.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Inaccurate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:46.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:49.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like when ruling forces change,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:53.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,they often spread stories like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:53.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:57.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,why didn't you say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.96,0:19:01.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This topic... is just too sensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:04.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I read this I meant to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.55,0:19:05.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:10.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been running around carefree without knowing anything all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:14.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been fun for you to watch, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.41,0:19:15.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:16.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:18.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:21.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I am calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:23.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My mind is going in circles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:26.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've known about Yoitsu all along, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:30.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:34.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew it when we first met!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.68,0:19:36.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, that explains a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:38.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:39.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.96,0:19:43.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,like weak, pitiable lambs after all, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:48.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it feel listening to me talk about returning to my hometown, completely ignorant that it's already gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:49.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My foolishness must have been cute to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:51.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So pitiable that you loved it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:54.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you let me indulge myself and treated me kindly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:20:02.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me to go back alone once we got to Niohira because you're already tired of me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:03.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:09.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've become alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:14.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one waiting for me at home anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:18.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've really become alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:21.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:25.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:25.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:28.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:35.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:38.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be alone anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:37.40,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:41.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:42.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mate with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:44.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:45.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alone now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:48.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I had a child, there'd be two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.71,0:20:52.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I'm in human form right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:53.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, won't you—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:54.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:05.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:07.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that kind of man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:08.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect anything from you to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:13.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:16.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone who truly loves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:22.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not panicking because you know you're going to trade me for 1000 silver, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:23.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.93,0:21:25.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.71,0:21:38.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
